            "@content":"Desk lamp with light toggle switch: this file builds a desk lamp that can be moved about. Dragging on the lamp base slides the lamp back and forth. Dragging on the lamp arms turns the lamp arm. Dragging on the lamp shade turns the lamp shade. Touching the lamp's light switch (on the top of the lamp shade) turns the lamp on and off."
